dev.nokee.platform.jni

Interface JniLibraryExtension

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BinaryAwareComponent, Component, DependencyAwareComponent<JavaNativeInterfaceLibraryComponentDependencies>, SourceAwareComponent<JavaNativeInterfaceLibrarySources>, TargetMachineAwareComponent, VariantAwareComponent<JniLibrary>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    JavaNativeInterfaceLibrary
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface JniLibraryExtension
extends DependencyAwareComponent<JavaNativeInterfaceLibraryComponentDependencies>, VariantAwareComponent<JniLibrary>, BinaryAwareComponent, TargetMachineAwareComponent, SourceAwareComponent<JavaNativeInterfaceLibrarySources>
    Configuration for a Java Native Interface (JNI) library, defining the dependencies that make up the library plus other settings.

    An instance of this type is added as a project extension by the JNI Library Plugin.

    Since:
    0.1
